longBusinessSummary: Cyon Exploration Ltd. acquires, explores for, and develops mineral properties in North America. The company holds a 100% interest in the Black Rock Canyon gold property that covers an area of approximately 3,894 acres located within the Cortez trend of the Battle Mountain Â Eureka belt. It also holds a 100% interest in the Aspen gold property that comprise 16 mineral claims in two aggregate groups covering an area of 7,450 acres located to the southwest of Vanderhoof in British Columbia, Canada. The company was formerly known as True Grit Resources Ltd. and changed its name to Cyon Exploration Ltd. in September 2020. Cyon Exploration Ltd. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
